#: addons/8_Islands.wad/addon:4 input:8 input:9 input:10 standard
msgid "8 Islands"
msgstr "8 Insels"

#: addons/8_Islands.wad/dirnames:4 input:4 standard
msgid "Add-On Maps"
msgstr "Verwiederns-Kaarten"

#: input:6 standard
msgid ""
"This map consists of 8 Islands. Mostly they have the same resources, but "
"which one? You have to find out and battle your enemies down. <br> <br>Don't "
"be slow - but also strong enough."
msgstr ""
"Deese Kaart bestaht ut 8 Inseln. Se hebben tomeest dat sülve Mineraal, aver "
"welkes? Du muttst ’t utfinnen un diene Feinden im Krieg manntjen. <br> "
"<br>Wees nich langsaam – man ok stark genoog."

#: input:7 input:13 standard
msgid "The middle is anytime good!"
msgstr "De Midde is alltiedens good!"
